      "Lean, the `•` operation is on the right of the matrix, and it is indeed continuous because the topology on matrices is the product topology (or matrix norm topology, equivalent for finite dimensions).\n\nBut perhaps we don't need to know about `wignerMatrixMap n` being measurable: we can instead try to directly prove that `wignerMatrixMap'` is measurable and then use scalar multiplication",
